text: This is a fantastic site, offerine both single and pairs of shoes, etc. especially for lymphedema patients, It is the ONLY place I have found shoes that fit my bandaged feet !! I am SO happy to finally find something to wear ,, I will definitely be ordering more !! Thank you for helping,
